welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Coolum Beach, where the ocean meets the charm of a small beach town. Known for its stunning beaches, vibrant local culture, and breathtaking scenery, we invite you to relax and explore all that Coolum has to offer."

terminals.description: The main terminal at Maroochydore Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Regional Terminal

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
